  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST THE PROLOGUE!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098890/extras/52a78a635533534b45e28e80850f1be9.poster.avif?t=1772475003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098890/extras/52a78a635533534b45e28e80850f1be9.webm?t=1772475003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A highly addictive survival crafting tower defense game!<br>Gather, craft, build turrets, shoot guns, and expand the land to defend against waves of enemies!</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gather resources and craft materials.<br></li><li> Craft useful equipment, turrets, and structures.<br></li><li> Beat waves of enemies using turrets and melee/ranged weapons.<br></li><li> Expand the land to reveal new resources and crafting recipes.<br></li><li> Tight and addicting gameplay loop.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098890/extras/52a78a635533534b45e28e80850f1be9.poster.avif?t=1772475003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098890/extras/52a78a635533534b45e28e80850f1be9.webm?t=1772475003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A highly addictive survival crafting tower defense game!<br>Gather, craft, build turrets, shoot guns, and expand the land to defend against waves of enemies!</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gather resources and craft materials.<br></li><li> Craft useful equipment, turrets, and structures.<br></li><li> Beat waves of enemies using turrets and melee/ranged weapons.<br></li><li> Expand the land to reveal new resources and crafting recipes.<br></li><li> Tight and addicting gameplay loop.</li></ul>",
